{"tid":1741031,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"國際戰線：反共似乎係無可避免","createTime":"2019-11-20T07:09:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T03:40:04.000Z","uid":193492,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"575625b8679581d9a7701f099107e799923e8e49","tid":1741031,"uid":193492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:09:09.000Z","msg":"我地成日笑藍絲「外國勢力」既論述<br />\n但係現實係好多外國左膠/共產黨支持者真係咁屈鳩我地<br />\n話美國支持香港係帝國主義<br />\n示威者歧視內地人同埋好暴力<br />\n外國做文宣既/twitter做嘢既可能要開始諗呢d意識形態<br />\n嘗試遊說佢地支持定要開火反駁？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/b-nl0Hklwvg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fb-nl0Hklwvg&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLGlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=d675c838\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/b-nl0Hklwvg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FoyjvmziZVc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFoyjvmziZVc&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLGlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=45ec3b8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FoyjvmziZVc</a>"},{"pid":"394cb4534112089ec8725d649810ef456c6f7eef","tid":1741031,"uid":193492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:10:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ef47599e1e26134e9cc6af94fe1a8259c4c9622","tid":1741031,"uid":193492,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:12:18.000Z","msg":"屌你老母你班左仔喺北美就大條道理話人種族歧視/帝國主義/戀殖/ 暴力<br />\n為咗撐共産主義國家就屈鳩我地<br />\n仆街"},{"pid":"8cdcfc253a325f79462599b14f82e53b42c71659","tid":1741031,"uid":193492,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:16:22.000Z","msg":"屌你係政府違憲、警渣濫權姦殺學生<br />\n錯既係我地？<br />\n之前見到有d懶喺睇透世事既仆街仔話可以唔同共產主義劃清界線<br />\n同我出黎"},{"pid":"aef6d8da7918974805d35f3d54ee7fdafe643d16","tid":1741031,"uid":321238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:21:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/026FRTK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F026FRTK.jpg&h=ba0c70f4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\